DeObia Oparei https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/DeObia_Oparei 0 DeObia Oparei (born 7 December 1971), also credited as Dhobi Oparei and Deobia Operei, is an English actor and playwright born in London, known for his role as the Gunner in Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides and as Thundarian in Your Highness.
